                            <div class="name">Planning support</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col">
                            <div class="excerpt">With your proposed designs in hand, you’re now ready to apply for planning approval. Our designers will always create proposed designs that give you the best chance of success, as well as satisfying your unique brief. If you already have planning in place, guidance will be provided on what happens next.
                                <br>Once you’re ready to proceed to the planning stage, they’ll hand you over to our in-house planning agents.
                                <br>If you want to visualise your space further, you might consider our 3D model package too. This allows you to see photorealistic images of your project, and even walkthrough the digitally rendered space. These models can be useful when making interior design decisions, or for luring in future buyers.</div>
